</p>
<center>Centered text</center>
<h2 id="an-example-flowchart-линия-lr">An example <strong>flowchart</strong> линия LR:</h2>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span><span class="lnt">5
</span><span class="lnt">6
</span><span class="lnt">7
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">{{&lt; mermaid &gt;}}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    graph LR
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    A[Толик] --&gt;|Плюс| B(Вовик)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    B --&gt; C{Родные Братья}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    C --&gt;|Один| D[Стрёмберг]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    C --&gt;|Другой| E[Дмитриев]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">{{&lt; /mermaid &gt;}}
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>renders as</p>
<div class="mermaid" id="id-1"></div>
<h3 id="диаграмма">Диаграмма</h3>
<a href="#some-interesting-title-">
  <h2 id="some-interesting-title-">Some Interesting Title - Диаграмма</h2>
</a>  

<p>Academic supports a Markdown extension for diagrams. You can enable this feature by toggling the <code>diagram</code> option in your <code>config/_default/params.toml</code> file or by adding <code>diagram: true</code> to your page front matter.</p>
<h2 id="an-example-flowchart----в-столбец-td">An example <strong>flowchart</strong> &ndash; в столбец TD:</h2>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span><span class="lnt">5
</span><span class="lnt">6
</span><span class="lnt">7
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">{{&lt; mermaid &gt;}}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    graph TD
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    A[Hard] --&gt;|Text| B(Round)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    B --&gt; C{Decision}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    C --&gt;|One| D[Result 1]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    C --&gt;|Two| E[Result 2]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">{{&lt; /mermaid &gt;}}
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>renders as</p>
<div class="mermaid" id="id-2"></div>
<h2 id="an-example-sequence-diagram">An example <strong>sequence diagram</strong>:</h2>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span><span class="lnt">5
</span><span class="lnt">6
</span><span class="lnt">7
</span><span class="lnt">8
</span><span class="lnt">9
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">sequenceDiagram
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    Alice-&gt;&gt;John: Hello John, how are you?
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    loop Healthcheck
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    John-&gt;&gt;John: Fight against hypochondria
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    end
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    Note right of John: Rational thoughts!
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    John--&gt;&gt;Alice: Great!
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    John-&gt;&gt;Bob: How about you?
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    Bob--&gt;&gt;John: Jolly good!
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>renders as</p>
<div class="mermaid" id="id-3"></div>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
